### GRACE governance tasks (full mode only)

If full mode, plan MUST include explicit tasks for:
- Update `MODULE_CONTRACT` header (VERSION bump, DEPENDS if new edge, MAP if new export, CHANGE_SUMMARY entry)
- Update `docs/development-plan.xml` `<interface>` / `<depends>` / `<observability>` / `<notes>` deltas
- Update `docs/knowledge-graph.xml` CrossLinks if cross-module edges added/removed
- Update `docs/verification-plan.xml` `<V-M-*>` if new scenarios / markers / test files
- Final gate: `grace lint --profile autonomous --path .` → 0/0

